## Performance Considerations

### Bundle Size
- **Vite** provides fast builds with tree-shaking
- **shadcn/ui** components are copy-pasted (not npm dependencies)
- Custom SVG charts (lighter than charting libraries)

### Rendering Performance
- Functional components with hooks
- No unnecessary re-renders (local state only)
- No global state thrashing

### Code Splitting
Could implement lazy loading for routes:
```typescript
const Index = lazy(() => import('./pages/Index'));
```

(Currently not needed for small single-page site)

