**Breakpoints:**
- No prefix = Mobile (< 640px)
- `sm:` = Small (640px+)
- `md:` = Medium (768px+)
- `lg:` = Large (1024px+)
- `xl:` = Extra Large (1280px+)
- `2xl:` = 2X Large (1536px+)

