### Avoid Large Components

If a component exceeds 300 lines:

1. **Extract sub-components**
   ```typescript
   // âœ— Bad - 500 line component
   export const ComplexPage = () => { /* ... */ }

   // âœ“ Good - split into smaller pieces
   export const ComplexPage = () => (
     <>
       <Header />
       <MainContent />
       <Sidebar />
       <Footer />
     </>
   );
   ```

2. **Create custom hooks**
   ```typescript
   // âœ— Bad - logic in component
   const MyComponent = () => {
     const [data, setData] = useState(null);
     useEffect(() => { /* complex logic */ }, []);
   }

   // âœ“ Good - logic in hook
   const useMyData = () => {
     const [data, setData] = useState(null);
     useEffect(() => { /* complex logic */ }, []);
     return data;
   };

   const MyComponent = () => {
     const data = useMyData();
   };
   ```

